title: Return of the Jaded
description:
Headliner:

► Return of the Jaded

[Returnofthejaded.com](Returnofthejaded.com)

The Canadian producer, DJ, and badman known as Return of the Jaded offers house music synonymous with superior sound quality, history, nostalgia, and cheeky rave culture. ROTJ has left a lasting impression upon superstars, tastemakers, and underground aficionados alike with support by Pete Tong, Nora En Pure, Afrojack, Alesso, Noizu, and more. His originals have charted Number 1 on Beatport over 8 times, with signature appearances on labels such as Purified, Techne, Repopulate Mars, Spinnin’ Deep, Sink or Swim, and many more.
